Q. The mysql driver is not currently installed

A. 解决是没有安装pdo-mysql这个扩展了，重新配置，加上–with-pdo-mysql=/usr/local/mysql/

file:///home/bob/workspace/kembo/doc/yamaha/localhost/php_cgi_i.html

./configure --with-mysql --with-pdo-mysql=/usr/sbin/

./configure --with-mysql --with-pdo-mysql OK

As of PHP 5.1.0, the CLI SAPI provides an interactive shell using the -a option if PHP is compiled with the --with-readline option.
./configure --with-mysql=mysqlnd --with-pdo-mysql=mysqlnd --with-readline --with-libedit

/usr/local/lib

http://localhost:10086/app/phpinfo001.php OK

bob@bob-Vostro-320:php$ sudo cp /usr/local/bin/php-cgi  /usr/local/apache2/cgi-bin/

bob@bob-Vostro-320:self$ ls -alh `which php`
